.DT
set_msgin
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
set_msgin

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_msgin -  This is the method used to set the current message to use when entering a room.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int set_msgin(string str)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^str%^RESET%^ - the message to print when entering a room
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/living/living.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This is the method used to set the current message to use when
entering a room.   A $N in the string will be expanded to the
name and a $F will be expanded to the from direction.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
/handlers/room_handler, query_msgin(), set_msgout()

.EP

